---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
    title="Services"
    description="專業的數據中心與企業機房解決方案"
    lang="en"
>
    <section class="services-container">
        <h2 class="section-title">Services</h2>
        <p class="section-description">
            T-Vetas Network 以高品質、適用且具成本效益的工程服務和最佳解決方案聞名，豐富的專案經驗讓我們在業界處於領先地位。
        </p>

        <div class="services-grid">
            <article class="service-card">
                <h3>Engineering Construction</h3>
                <p class="card-description">Supply customers with telecom services such as design/installation required for telecom rooms/data centers.</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        <a href="/en/ehs" class="vendor-link">EHS (環境、健康與安全管理)</a>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <a href="/en/bim" class="vendor-link">BIM/CAD 工程設計與建模</a>
                    </li>
                    <li>數據中心建置</li>
                    <li>電力系統規劃與施工</li>
                    <li>結構化佈線系統施工</li>
                </ul>
            </article>

            <article class="service-card">
                <h3>Materials</h3>
                <p class="card-description">Provide customers with the construction materials.</p>
                <ul>
                  <li><a href="/en/materials#corning" class="vendor-link">CORNING (康寧)</a></li>
                  <li><a href="/en/materials#ciena" class="vendor-link">Ciena</a></li>
                  <li><a href="/en/materials#infinera" class="vendor-link">Infinera</a></li>
                  <li><a href="/en/materials#schneider" class="vendor-link">Schneider (施耐德), APC</a></li>
                  <li><a href="/en/materials#panduit" class="vendor-link">Panduit</a></li>
                  <li><a href="/en/materials#afl" class="vendor-link">AFL</a></li>
                  <li><a href="/en/materials#jpc" class="vendor-link">JPC</a></li>
                  <li><a href="/en/materials#dell" class="vendor-link">Dell</a></li>
                </ul>
            </article>

            <article class="service-card">
                <h3>Certificate</h3>
                <p class="card-description">Certification is a way to demonstrate the quality of a company's installers/testers. Our company has certifications from many multinational companies.</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><a href="/en/certificates#corning" class="vendor-link">CORNING (康寧)</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/en/certificates#ciena" class="vendor-link">Ciena</a></li>
                    <li>Infinera</li>
                    <li><a href="/en/certificates#panduit" class="vendor-link">Panduit</a></li>
                </ul>
            </article>

            <article class="service-card">
                <h3>Network solution</h3>
                <p class="card-description">We provide different network solutions according to customer needs.</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>IP network</li>
                    <li>SDH/WDM network</li>
                    <li>Wifi network</li>
                </ul>
            </article>

            <article class="service-card">
                <h3>Maintain</h3>
                <p class="card-description">We provides smart hand services for many companies, ensuring that customers' services can operate normally 365 days a year.</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>RMA 故障設備更換服務</li>
                    <li>5x8 基本維護支援</li>
                    <li>7x24 全天候緊急支援</li>
                    <li>結構化佈線系統維護</li>
                    <li>定期巡檢與預防性維護</li>
                    <li>遠端技術支援與諮詢</li>
                    <li>現場故障排除服務</li>
                    <li>系統效能監控與優化</li>
                </ul>
            </article>

        </div>
    </section>
</Layout>

<style>
.services-container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 5rem 2rem;
}

.section-title {
    font-size: 1.5rem;        /* 從 2rem 改小 */
    font-weight: 600;         /* 從 bold 改為 600 */
    text-align: center;
    color: #1A2A47;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
}

.section-description {
    text-align: center;
    color: #4a5568;
    font-size: 1rem;         /* 加入字體大小設定 */
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto 3rem auto;
    line-height: 1.6;
}

.services-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 2.5rem;
}

.service-card {
    background: white;
    padding: 1.8rem;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 15px -3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    transition: transform 0.2s ease-in-out;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
}

/* 工程施工卡片 - 藍色主題 */
.service-card:nth-child(1) {
    border-top: 4px solid #44B3FF;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom right, #ffffff, #f0f9ff);
}

/* 物料供應卡片 - 綠色主題 */
.service-card:nth-child(2) {
    border-top: 4px solid #48BB78;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom right, #ffffff, #f0fff4);
}

/* 證書卡片 - 金色主題 */
.service-card:nth-child(3) {
    border-top: 4px solid #ECC94B;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom right, #ffffff, #fffff0);
}

/* 網路解決方案卡片 - 紫色主題 */
.service-card:nth-child(4) {
    border-top: 4px solid #9F7AEA;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom right, #ffffff, #faf5ff);
}

/* 維護卡片 - 橘色主題 */
.service-card:nth-child(5) {
    border-top: 4px solid #ED8936;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom right, #ffffff, #fffaf0);
}

.service-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 20px -3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
}

.service-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.1rem;       /* 從 1.25rem 改小 */
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    position: relative;
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
}

.service-card h3::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 40px;
    height: 2px;
    background: currentColor;
    opacity: 0.3;
}

.card-description {
    color: #4a5568;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    font-size: 0.9rem;      /* 從 0.95rem 改小 */
}

.service-card ul {
    list-style-type: disc;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    color: #4a5568;
    font-size: 0.9rem;      /* 加入字體大小設定 */
}

.service-card li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
}

.full-width {
    grid-column: span 2;
}

.highlight-text {
    color: #4a5568;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
}

.vendor-link {
    color: #44B3FF;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 0.2s;
}

.vendor-link:hover {
    color: #FF7A00;
    text-decoration: underline;
}

@media (max-width: 768px) {
    .services-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .full-width {
        grid-column: span 1;
    }

    .services-container {
        padding: 3rem 1rem;
    }
}
</style>